content:
Ok folks, let’s slow it down with this question:

Lifetime announces a made for TV Movie about the Trumps. What’s it called?

I got another one:

The Worst Wing
I don't know what they'd call it, but it would have to be something like a Satanic cross between the Beverly Hillbillies and Keeping up with the Kardashians.  My stomach turns just thinking about it.
That could be it "tRUmps: As The Stomach Turns"
The Trumps: First Family Reunion Behind Bars,pic.twitter.com/InyLVA1sl8
Orange is the new White House
Because video would make me want to,pic.twitter.com/a1DdeSBIGU
The Chronicles of Nincompoopia: The voyage of the Dumb Treaders.
The Lowest Rated Show on Lifetime.
Or SlumLord Billionaire, which would work for any of the Trump family members
I like the title Chris Hayes has been using on MSNBC - - All the President’s Mess
When he looked up at the eclipse, why didn't the sun gods just strike him down into a pile of salt?? Crisis over.
I really don’t care, do you?

Or how about Daddy diddles daughter.....
Too subtle?
He kinda makes me wish abortion was retroactive!!!
LOSERS would be a good title. Oh, and how about the old Cher song from 1971? Gypsies, Tramps and Thieves?
OMG I haven’t been this happy and giggly in a LONG time! Keep ‘em coming!!

Close Encounters of the Turd Kind

(I know I’m ignoring the Lifetime thing. Sorry.)
Raiders of the Lost Email Server
Please tell me you are a copywriter. These are GOLD
STOP IT! I can’t laugh any more! My stomach muscles are convulsing
"Trumpery" (which is an actual word no longer in use which means "showy but worthless").
Sex, Lies and Videotape...oh wait...Part 2...Cronyism, Crime and Corruption
How We Betrayed Our Country and Made Millions Doing It!
Hey now don't be disrespecting the Walkers! They didn't do nothing..
Ugh, so played out... like my mom type-a played out
The Death of a Nation: a history of the trump WH.
The Decline and Fall of the Trump Empire
You must be thinking of Trump's version of "Caligula."
Yeah.. I think we've all earned our $150K by now,pic.twitter.com/dIYW5hWG2e

"Orange Is the New Traitor"
Followed by the Pence film: "Mother May I Sleep With Fascists?"

It’s lifetime so.....

How I banged my daughter
Creepy father
My father the rapist
His supporters remind me of the movie Idiocracy!!
The many whores of Donald Trump
Was that a reference to moonlighting? if so, nice one. if not, what inspired it?
Maybe not the most creative, but I think “Psycho” works.

“How to Destroy America in 90 Days”
Featuring an old creepy turtle who sells cocaine on the side, a psychotic elf who throws children in jail,a rancid Wisc cheesehead who tries to send all Veterans to live on the street & starring a bloated orange mutant who only knows 8,9 words.
Things To Do in DC When You’re an Asshole
From the White House to the Big House, a story of America’s First Family of Crime.

Ok, y'all are brilliant! I can't top any of these, but I can add that the "based on a true story" tag will need an asterisk that says "Sort of true...this family wouldn't know the truth if it was a gold-plated golf ball. But we did our best."
Lordy there were tapes. The rise and fall of Putin's Poodle.
Cloudy with a Chance of No Balls

Russia has taken over by the time Lifetime releases this movie!! Ha! “Русский в белом доме ... Настоящий американский кошмар”                                                Translation: “A Russian In The White House...A True American Nightmare”

Asset Zero.

"You Can't Make Me Watch Anything On Lifetime!"
white trash in the white house

Unwatchable.

The Trump Show is already old and I want it to end.

Don't want to sit through it again.
When bad things happen to good Americans
